<div class="content"><p> </p><p>The VDS_DRIVE_LETTER_FLAG enumeration defines the set of
valid flags for a <span><a href="8eef5d42-22d7-4302-aed9-12face91505a#gt_1b153cd0-e3f3-4383-bc66-d5ad482c9766" data-linktype="relative-path">drive letter</a></span>.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef enum _VDS_DRIVE_LETTER_FLAG
 {
   VDS_DLF_NON_PERSISTENT = 0x00000001
 } VDS_DRIVE_LETTER_FLAG;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>VDS_DLF_NON_PERSISTENT:  </b>If set, the drive
letter no longer appears after the computer is restarted.</p></div>